title: Five, four, three, two, one birds away
brief_description: In a simulated attack by a Jindivik unmanned target aircraft, the destroyer H.M.A.S. Hobart demonstrates its new electronic detection and defence systems, firing a Tarter guided missile. Part of the Navy in Focus series.
